Develop a single-page React application designed as a Todo list. Design & Layout: Header: The top of the page should have a prominent header titled "Todo items." Addition Icon: Right next to the header, there should be a plus sign (+) icon. Adding Todos: Input Field: Clicking the plus sign should reveal an input field. Submit Button: Alongside the input field, provide a button to submit the todo. Active Todo Items Table: Display a table beneath the header. Columns: Date Added, Description, Action with minus sign (-) icon. Completed Todo Items Table: Another table for completed tasks. Columns: Date Added, Description, Date Completed. Styling: Zebra Striping in both tables. Animations for adding or moving tasks. Notifications for task actions. Responsiveness: Ensure app works on all devices.